{
  "page": "Did you know/119",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>, despite having had six wives in his lifetime (<a href=\"/index.php/Ceryse_Hightower\" title=\"Ceryse Hightower\">Ceryse Hightower</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Harroway\" title=\"Alys Harroway\">Alys Harroway</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Tyanna_of_the_Tower\" title=\"Tyanna of the Tower\">Tyanna of the Tower</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Elinor_Costayne\" title=\"Elinor Costayne\">Elinor Costayne</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aenys I)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Westerling_(wife_of_Maegor_I)\" title=\"Jeyne Westerling (wife of Maegor I)\">Jeyne Westerling</a>), had no official living issue?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/119&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP l